<div class="overlay" id="m-ed"><div class="modal" style="width:560px"><div class="mhd"><div class="mtitle">Entscheidungsvorlage ГўвӮ¬вҖқ Drift</div><button class="mx" onclick="cm('m-ed')">ГўЕ“вҖў</button></div><div class="mbody"><div style="background:var(--neg-lt);border:1px solid rgba(153,27,27,0.12);border-radius:var(--r);padding:8px;margin-bottom:12px;font-size:11px;line-height:1.6">Aktienquote 53% vs. Soll 45%. Drift +8.2%. Seit 14. November verletzt.</div><div class="fs">Optionen</div><div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px"><div style="border:1px solid var(--b1);border-radius:var(--r);padding:9px;cursor:pointer" onclick="this.style.borderColor='var(--n6)';this.style.background='var(--n0)'"><div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:3px">ГўЕ“вҖң Option A ГўвӮ¬вҖқ ZuflГғВјsse umlenken (empfohlen)</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--n6);line-height:1.4">CHF 155k in Anleihen &amp; LiquiditГғВӨt. Organische Normalisierung 12ГўвӮ¬вҖң18 Monate.</div></div><div style="border:1px solid var(--b1);border-radius:var(--r);padding:9px;cursor:pointer" onclick="this.style.borderColor='var(--n6)';this.style.background='var(--n0)'"><div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:3px">Option B ГўвӮ¬вҖқ Teilverkauf Aktien CHF 300k</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--n6);line-height:1.4">Sofortige Normalisierung. Steuerfolgen prГғВјfen.</div></div><div style="border:1px solid var(--b1);border-radius:var(--r);padding:9px;cursor:pointer" onclick="this.style.borderColor='var(--n6)';this.style.background='var(--n0)'"><div style="font-size:11px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:3px">Option C ГўвӮ¬вҖқ Drift tolerieren (dokumentiert)</div><div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--n6);line-height:1.4">Mit BegrГғВјndung weiteres Quartal. Kundenkommunikation notwendig.</div></div></div></div><div class="mfooter"><button class="btn" onclick="cm('m-ed')">Schliessen</button><button class="btn-p" onclick="cm('m-ed');alert('Entscheid dokumentiert.'